00:00:08.839 --> 00:00:10.259
días los ataques militares

00:00:10.259 --> 00:00:11.919
contra la infraestructura energética

00:00:11.919 --> 00:00:13.460
de Irán. Decisión que

00:00:13.460 --> 00:00:13.839
se produce

00:00:13.839 --> 00:00:15.240
tras un ultimatum previo

00:00:15.240 --> 00:00:16.239
